-- Backend --

I want to be able to see where a post originated.
I want to be able to tell the difference between cards and notifications
I want to be able to remove duplicate posts

-- GUI --

As a user, I want to have a desktop notification when certain events happen
As a user, I want to be able to look at my feeds from the main page.
As a user, I want to be able to see data about posts I make

